N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4108.5 - Two-year-old distances; heats

State Regulations

No two-year-old shall be permitted to start in any dash, heat or race exceeding one mile, nor shall a two-year-old be permitted to start
in more than two heats, dashes, or races in any single day. Notes
